		<title>肚子餓的時候智商會下線？橘貓狂舔「假肉泥」絲毫沒察覺哪裡出問題！ </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/18/%e8%82%9a%e5%ad%90%e9%a4%93%e7%9a%84%e6%99%82%e5%80%99%e6%99%ba%e5%95%86%e6%9c%83%e4%b8%8b%e7%b7%9a%ef%bc%9f%e6%a9%98%e8%b2%93%e7%8b%82%e8%88%94%e3%80%8c%e5%81%87%e8%82%89%e6%b3%a5%e3%80%8d%e7%b5%b2/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
